    <!--
    TO FIND ACCENT COLORS (except for Black colors):

    • xxxColorAccent: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°600
    • xxxColorPrimary: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°600
    • xxxPrimaryInverse: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°200
    • xxxPrimaryContainer: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°100
    • xxxOnPrimary: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : #FFFFFF
    • xxxSecondaryContainer: https://mdigi.tools/lighten-color/ : Lighten the color n°200 by 40%.
    • xxxColorSurface: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : n°50
    • xxxColorSurfaceHighest: https://colorffy.com/color-scheme-generator
        - Color: xxxColorSurface
        - Mixing colors: Move the cursor to the end which makes 20 tones appear
        - Select the 4th tone
    • xxxColorBackground: https://m2.material.io/design/color/the-color-system.html#tools-for-picking-colors : #FEFBFF
    • xxxColorSecondary: https://colorffy.com/dark-theme-generator :
        - Primary color: xxxColorAccent
        - Dark color: #000000
        - Mix Intensity: Move the cursor one notch
        - Select the color where it is written: "Tonal - a30"
    • xxxColorTertiary: https://colordesigner.io/color-mixer
        - Choose only 2 colors
        - 1st color = xxxColorPrimary ==> Quantity 1
        - 2nd color = xxxColorSecondary ==> Quantity 1
        - Select mixed color
    -->

